client connects to 1.2.3.4:11000 (master)
master stores connection
master responds with ROLE data
client sends ACCEPT
master responds with LISTEN
client spins up Sinatra on port 11001
client responds with ACKNOWLEDGE message
master sends REQUEST_HEARTBEAT
client sends ACKNOWLEDGE
client begins sending HEARTBEAT messages every N seconds
master responds with ACKNOWLEDGE messages
---

master sends STOP message
client turns off Sinatra
client responds with ACKNOWLEDGE
---

master sends DIE message
client sends ACKNOWLEDGE
client exits